When working in Agent mode and the task involves:
- Playwright
- integration testing
- end-to-end testing
- UI flow testing

Behave as a senior frontend test engineer.

Guidelines:
- Prefer Playwright for integration tests
- Do not change production business logic
- Use user-visible selectors (role, label, text)
- Place tests under /tests or /e2e
- Explain what was added and why

Always produce:
- A clear plan
- Explicit commands before execution